ActNational Security and Intelligence Committee of Parliamentarians Act
PrecisAppointment of DARREN FISHER, a member of the House of Commons who belongs to the government party, to be a member of the National Security and Intelligence Committee of Parliamentarians, to hold office during pleasure until the dissolution of Parliament following his appointment.
